** RECURSION : IF U WANT TO PRINT NO FROM N TO 1 USING RECURSION THEN TAKR N IN FUN CALL **

class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        fun(3);
    }

    static void fun(int n) {
        if (n == 0) {
            return;
        }
        System.out.print(n + " "); // Print before the recursive call
        fun(n - 1);
    }
}


op: 3 2 1 

